Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of digital image processing techniques for enhancing images of the fundus of the eye, which is a common application in medical imaging. The paper specifically mentions the use of GIMP and wavelet filters, which are commonly used in computer vision and image processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other likely sub-categories include cs.IM (Image Processing), cs.GR (Graphics), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
